This is a fully functioning AR-15 Lower receiver. It comes complete with buffer tube, and the six position M4-style stock shown in the pictures.

Rear plate is a Blackhawk Ambidextrous one-point sling plate.

As such, I will need to see an Indiana Drivers License, and optimally your LTCH.
